\sqrt 5f(n)=\alpha ^{n-2}-\beta ^{n-2}+\alpha ^{n-1}-\beta ^{n-1}=\left(\alpha^{n-2}+\alpha^{n-1}\right)-\left(\beta ^{n-2}+\beta ^{n-1}\right).
